{"tid":2352708,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"以《South Park》Cosplay 聞名《魔獸世界》的宅男玩家因武漢肺炎病逝","createTime":"2021-01-04T08:01:29.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-04T08:03:13.000Z","uid":49208,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"f8469a05622717679508e0079da2f8f7bcb692ad","tid":2352708,"uid":49208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:01:29.000Z","msg":"以 Cosplay《南方四賤客》宅男聞名的《魔獸世界》玩家 NWBZPWNR 今日傳出因嚴重特殊傳染性肺炎（COVID-2019，又稱武漢肺炎、新冠肺炎）而過世的消息。<br />\n <br />\n  《魔獸世界》玩家 NWBZPWNR 本名為 Jarod Nandin，他在 2013 年 BlizzCon 中 Cosplay 了、由《南方四賤客》推出的《魔獸世界》小短劇中的宅男，而其作品受到全球粉絲廣傳與熱烈迴響。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/88/7576c5a470a164fc21d5fbbf921b37g5.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F88%2F7576c5a470a164fc21d5fbbf921b37g5.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=39f73b38&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://p2.bahamut.com.tw/B/2KU/89/791de5e2adc47583998f8acf261b37h5.JPG?w=1000\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fp2.bahamut.com.tw%2FB%2F2KU%2F89%2F791de5e2adc47583998f8acf261b37h5.JPG%3Fw%3D1000&h=3b5d2e2d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n <br />\n  2020 年 12 月 19 日，NWBZPWNR 在推特上發文因為胸痛而送急診，四天後接著確認自己被確診了武漢肺炎，並仍保持樂觀態度表示「別擔心，我會撐過去的。」之後在推特上不定時更新病情狀況，引發呼吸併發症等問題。<br />\n <br />\n<br />\n <br />\n  今日稍早國外媒體 Wowhead 報導指出，NWBZPWNR 不幸離世，NWBZPWNR 的許多朋友也紛紛在推特上表達哀悼之意。其中，常受邀擔任 BlizzCon 主持人的 Michele Morrow 也呼應了《南方四賤客》的《魔獸世界》小短劇中的劇情，貼出舉起 USB 的照片，並表示貼出了「以他（NWBZPWNR ）的榮耀舉起『千真劍』」，同時願 NWBZPWNR 安息。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />RIP<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46009efe45077d68bc9c81cf32a740da3e53278e","tid":2352708,"uid":8014,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T08:03:13.000Z","msg":"死肥仔有長期病<br />\n<br />\n武肺just a flu<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}